# python:3.12-slim(Debian) base image OS package CVEs.
# Risk-accepted 2026-07-12: ci_sandbox is a FastAPI app that does not invoke
# perl/gzip/acl/ncurses/util-linux at runtime - these are incidental base OS
# packages, not part of our app's attack surface. Several are also
# vendor "fix_deferred" (Debian has chosen not to patch yet), so no
# upstream fix exists to pull in via apt upgrade.
# Re-review this file whenever the Dockerfile base image changes.
#
# Re-reviewed 2026-07-15 after pinning python:3.12-slim to a digest (PR #16):
# two new perl-base CVEs appeared under the same already-accepted rationale
# above (perl is not invoked by ci_sandbox at runtime).

